{"talks": [{"code": "XCABN8", "id": 8523, "title": "Google Earth Engine & Python", "abstract": "O tutorial curto de Google Earth Engine & Python apresenta o Google Earth Engine (GEE), uma plataforma de escala global para an\u00e1lises geoespaciais, acess\u00edvel em JavaScript e Python.", "speakers": ["FJXRUE"], "track": 84, "start": "2026-06-05T08:30:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-05T12:00:00-03:00", "room": 65, "duration": 210, "updated": "2026-05-05T23:20:46.690714+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "PGCXJN", "id": 8525, "title": "Python para Cidadania: Dados da C\u00e2mara em ano eleitoral.", "abstract": "Tutorial pr\u00e1tico de an\u00e1lise de dados p\u00fablicos com Python usando a API da C\u00e2mara dos Deputados. Vamos coletar, analisar e visualizar dados legislativos em um notebook no Google Colab.", "speakers": ["TWS3FV"], "track": 83, "start": "2026-06-05T08:30:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-05T12:00:00-03:00", "room": 67, "duration": 210, "updated": "2026-05-05T23:20:47.588020+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "JF3K3F", "id": 8526, "title": "An\u00e1lise de Dados Geoespaciais", "abstract": "Tutorial de an\u00e1lise geoespacial com Python, abordando dados geogr\u00e1ficos, mapas e m\u00e9todos anal\u00edticos para compreender dados georreferenciados e assim, gerar hip\u00f3teses.", "speakers": ["J8LYJ7"], "track": 83, "start": "2026-06-05T14:00:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-05T17:30:00-03:00", "room": 67, "duration": 210, "updated": "2026-05-05T11:08:14.617652+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "WKLA8H", "id": 8522, "title": "Introdu\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e0 Arquitetura Orientada a Eventos com FastStream", "abstract": "Neste minicurso, faremos uma introdu\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e0 arquitetura orientada a eventos, utilizando a biblioteca FastStream em conjunto com o message broker RabbitMQ.", "speakers": ["JUUC7E"], "track": 84, "start": "2026-06-05T14:00:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-05T17:30:00-03:00", "room": 68, "duration": 210, "updated": "2026-05-05T23:19:23.037418+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "PGHKG7", "id": 8524, "title": "Descubra emo\u00e7\u00f5es em textos com NLP, LLM\u2019s e ML", "abstract": "Descubra como funcionam as emo\u00e7\u00f5es em textos utilizando t\u00e9cnicas de NLP, LLM\u2019s e ML. Um tutorial 100% m\u00e3o na massa, o objetivo \u00e9 apresentar desde os conceitos at\u00e9 a aplica\u00e7\u00e3o pr\u00e1tica com um aprendizad", "speakers": ["EAKK9E"], "track": 84, "start": "2026-06-05T14:00:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-05T17:30:00-03:00", "room": 65, "duration": 210, "updated": "2026-05-05T11:09:03.700466+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"id": 8589, "title": {"pt-br": "Credenciamento + Coffee break"}, "start": "2026-06-06T11:00:00Z", "end": "2026-06-06T09:15:00-03:00", "room": 66, "slot_type": "break"}, {"id": 8549, "title": {"pt-br": "Abertura"}, "start": "2026-06-06T12:15:00Z", "end": "2026-06-06T09:30:00-03:00", "room": 66, "slot_type": "break"}, {"code": "WJMGYZ", "id": 8541, "title": "Seu app precisa mesmo da Internet? Local-first c/ Reticulum", "abstract": "Precisamos mesmo da internet para tudo? Uma provoca\u00e7\u00e3o pr\u00e1tica com Reticulum mostrando comunica\u00e7\u00e3o local-first funcionando sem servidores, IP fixo ou conectividade cont\u00ednua.", "speakers": ["7ZVMTD"], "track": 83, "start": "2026-06-06T09:30:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-06T10:15:00-03:00", "room": 69, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-14T17:45:36.384955+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "XDGFQA", "id": 8527, "title": "Do Texto ao Dado: O Uso de PLN no Contexto da Educa\u00e7\u00e3o", "abstract": "Como a IA pode ir al\u00e9m de uma simples nota e oferecer feedbacks que realmente ensinam? Vamos explorar os bastidores do desenvolvimento de aplica\u00e7\u00f5es de corre\u00e7\u00e3o de reda\u00e7\u00f5es do ENEM.", "speakers": ["KFYJ9G"], "track": 84, "start": "2026-06-06T09:30:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-06T10:15:00-03:00", "room": 66, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-15T09:56:10.201743+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "UUAQDN", "id": 8543, "title": "Como as humanas podem salvar os humanos do impacto da IA", "abstract": "As incertezas da tecnologia passaram a dominar a ansiedade dos pr\u00f3prios engenheiros. Talvez a resposta para esse dilema n\u00e3o esteja na tecnologia. Como os humanos salvar\u00e3o os humanos dos rob\u00f4s?", "speakers": ["X3T8HM"], "track": 82, "start": "2026-06-06T10:20:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-06T11:05:00-03:00", "room": 69, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-14T17:45:27.357673+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "EDQKJX", "id": 8540, "title": "Joins no Spark: Broadcast, Shuffle e Sort Merge", "abstract": "Compare as estrat\u00e9gias de JOIN no Pyspark e aprenda a escolher a ideal para cada situa\u00e7\u00e3o, otimizando performance e recursos", "speakers": ["P938DV"], "track": 84, "start": "2026-06-06T10:20:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-06T11:05:00-03:00", "room": 66, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-14T17:45:21.105736+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"id": 8557, "title": {"pt-br": "APyB"}, "start": "2026-06-06T14:05:00Z", "end": "2026-06-06T11:15:00-03:00", "room": 66, "slot_type": "break"}, {"id": 8596, "title": {"pt-br": "Palestras rel\u00e2mpago"}, "start": "2026-06-06T14:15:00Z", "end": "2026-06-06T11:30:00-03:00", "room": 66, "slot_type": "break"}, {"id": 8545, "title": {"pt-br": "Kiko"}, "start": "2026-06-06T14:30:00Z", "end": "2026-06-06T12:30:00-03:00", "room": 66, "slot_type": "break"}, {"code": "TJXKDA", "id": 8532, "title": "9 anos de ensino de Redes com Python", "abstract": "Relato de 9 anos usando Python como linguagem principal nas pr\u00e1ticas de Redes de Computadores \u2014 onde d\u00e1 conta de tudo, e onde foi preciso buscar alternativas.", "speakers": ["H78P9N"], "track": 83, "start": "2026-06-06T12:30:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-06T13:15:00-03:00", "room": 69, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-15T09:55:08.178926+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "LSQREJ", "id": 8533, "title": "Movendo Icebergs Para Um Floco de Neve", "abstract": "De monolito com Iceberg a Snowflake: a jornada real de uma migra\u00e7\u00e3o \u2014 arquitetura, decis\u00f5es t\u00e9cnicas, ganhos de desempenho e as li\u00e7\u00f5es que s\u00f3 a pr\u00e1tica ensina.", "speakers": ["AWRK7D"], "track": 84, "start": "2026-06-06T14:00:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-06T14:45:00-03:00", "room": 69, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-05T11:12:48.235934+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "AFLKF8", "id": 8530, "title": "Como criar e manter comunidades? Por uma pylady", "abstract": "O que \u00e9 preciso para criar uma comunidade em tecnologia? O que \u00e9 essencial para manter uma comunidade ativa? Um papo sobre pessoas, cria\u00e7\u00e3o de amizades, conhecimento t\u00e9cnico e networking.", "speakers": ["9B937P"], "track": 82, "start": "2026-06-06T14:00:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-06T14:45:00-03:00", "room": 66, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-15T09:56:17.647100+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "KT9YE3", "id": 8538, "title": "Computa\u00e7\u00e3o distribu\u00edda em Python com Dask", "abstract": "Vamos conhecer Dask. O framework para computa\u00e7\u00e3o distribu\u00edda entre v\u00e1rias m\u00e1quinas escrito em Python.", "speakers": ["XFKA87"], "track": 85, "start": "2026-06-06T14:50:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-06T15:35:00-03:00", "room": 69, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-15T09:58:34.564000+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "U3DP8D", "id": 8534, "title": "Magias ao vivo: a arquitetura do T\u00e9o Me Why", "abstract": "Essa palestra tem como objetivo dar luz \u00e0 arquitura e decis\u00f5es de tecnologia que tivemos ao construir o ecosistema do T\u00e9o Me Why ao vivo, sempre com prioridade a entrega de valor para a comunidade.", "speakers": ["GTCE7N"], "track": 84, "start": "2026-06-06T15:40:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-06T16:25:00-03:00", "room": 66, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-13T00:31:03.632623+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"id": 8558, "title": {"pt-br": "Coffee break"}, "start": "2026-06-06T19:25:00Z", "end": "2026-06-06T16:45:00-03:00", "room": 66, "slot_type": "break"}, {"id": 8559, "title": {"pt-br": "Palestras rel\u00e2mpago"}, "start": "2026-06-06T19:45:00Z", "end": "2026-06-06T17:10:00-03:00", "room": 66, "slot_type": "break"}, {"id": 8546, "title": {"pt-br": "Andressa"}, "start": "2026-06-06T20:10:00Z", "end": "2026-06-06T18:10:00-03:00", "room": 66, "slot_type": "break"}, {"id": 8566, "title": {"pt-br": "Coffee break"}, "start": "2026-06-07T12:00:00Z", "end": "2026-06-07T09:30:00-03:00", "room": 66, "slot_type": "break"}, {"id": 8560, "title": {"pt-br": "Abertura"}, "start": "2026-06-07T12:30:00Z", "end": "2026-06-07T09:35:00-03:00", "room": 66, "slot_type": "break"}, {"code": "GFFGWV", "id": 8535, "title": "Como um sistema de recomenda\u00e7\u00e3o decide o que voc\u00ea v\u00ea", "abstract": "Sistemas de recomenda\u00e7\u00e3o podem ser constru\u00eddos com diversas abordagens, desde heur\u00edsticas simples at\u00e9 deep learning. Nesta palestra, vamos conhecer como diferentes modelos de recomenda\u00e7\u00e3o funcionam!", "speakers": ["AJ8TCF"], "track": 84, "start": "2026-06-07T09:35:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-07T10:20:00-03:00", "room": 66, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-14T17:48:06.072873+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "JQMZ3M", "id": 8565, "title": "Como Python facilita a vida de um engenheiro geot\u00e9cnico", "abstract": "Essa atividade visa apresentar aplica\u00e7\u00f5es do Python na Engenharia Geot\u00e9cnica nos \u00e2mbitos do ensino-aprendizagem, da pesquisa e da ind\u00fastria; desde o ponto de vista de um pesquisador da EESC-USP.", "speakers": ["PDYWJM"], "track": 84, "start": "2026-06-07T09:35:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-07T10:20:00-03:00", "room": 69, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-14T17:48:08.032746+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "NBVMNM", "id": 8528, "title": "Pula a fogueira iai\u00e1: Python no combate \u00e0s queimadas no RJ", "abstract": "Como o uso do Python para a implementa\u00e7\u00e3o e automa\u00e7\u00e3o de um sistema de alertas de queimadas (De Olho no Verde - Queimadas) vem ajudando o Rio de Janeiro no combate \u00e0s queimadas.", "speakers": ["G3ZVNS"], "track": 83, "start": "2026-06-07T10:25:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-07T11:10:00-03:00", "room": 66, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-14T17:47:56.140361+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "ZWFPDR", "id": 8539, "title": "TDD na Pr\u00e1tica: Uma demonstra\u00e7\u00e3o com Django", "abstract": "H\u00e1 duas maneiras de minimizar complexidade no desenvolvimento de software: modelagem e testes. Nesta palestra, explicamos o que \u00e9 Test Driven Development (TDD) e realizamos uma demonstra\u00e7\u00e3o com Django", "speakers": ["EYVJCW"], "track": 83, "start": "2026-06-07T10:25:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-07T11:10:00-03:00", "room": 69, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-14T17:47:59.016910+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"id": 8547, "title": {"pt-br": "Moacir"}, "start": "2026-06-07T14:30:00Z", "end": "2026-06-07T12:30:00-03:00", "room": 66, "slot_type": "break"}, {"code": "YPYPCB", "id": 8529, "title": "Revelando padr\u00f5es em redes complexas com Python", "abstract": "Nesta palestra apresento como usar Python e An\u00e1lise Topol\u00f3gica de Dados para identificar padr\u00f5es em redes complexas, explorando a extra\u00e7\u00e3o e interpreta\u00e7\u00e3o de estruturas topol\u00f3gicas.", "speakers": ["A8S7FC"], "track": 84, "start": "2026-06-07T14:00:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-07T14:45:00-03:00", "room": 66, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-13T00:53:47.816771+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "TCUCQJ", "id": 8542, "title": "Construindo uma Cultura de Code Review", "abstract": "O que voc\u00ea avalia na revis\u00e3o de um c\u00f3digo? Faz isso at\u00e9 nas suas pr\u00f3prias PRs? Vou abordar a import\u00e2ncia do code review para a colabora\u00e7\u00e3o e passagem de conhecimento com dicas para autores e revisores", "speakers": ["PPXL7G"], "track": 83, "start": "2026-06-07T14:00:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-07T14:45:00-03:00", "room": 69, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-13T00:31:28.030778+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "J8YJZU", "id": 8536, "title": "Testes Baseados em Propriedades", "abstract": "Essa palestra aborda um tipo de teste chamado de \"teste de propriedades\" que muda o jeito de escrevermos testes do nosso c\u00f3digo, permitindo que n\u00f3s testemos uma \u00e1rea maior das poss\u00edveis entradas.", "speakers": ["8TYELR"], "track": 84, "start": "2026-06-07T14:50:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-07T15:35:00-03:00", "room": 69, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-13T00:39:22.855584+00:00", "state": null, "content_locale": "pt-br", "do_not_record": null}, {"code": "8ELYMS", "id": 8544, "title": "Django aos 20: velho demais ou maduro o suficiente?", "abstract": "Django tem 20 anos e zero hype mas continua entregando. ORM, auth, migrations, admin e um ecossistema imenso, tudo pronto.", "speakers": ["NPTGX3"], "track": 83, "start": "2026-06-07T14:50:00-03:00", "end": "2026-06-07T15:35:00-03:00", "room": 66, "duration": 45, "updated": "2026-05-13T00:36:25.